        "created_at": "2025-01-19T12:49:13.415Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I have gotten offers for this wine, it look intriguing . I like St Aubin wines and they used to be really quite undervalued, but the prices have crept up year after year. Is this wine a blend? A \u201ckitchen sink\u201d chardonnay of parcels or barrels that didn\u2019t make the cut? Couldn\u2019t find much information about it. Thought I would check in on the collective wisdom here</p>",
