        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/67e7ee/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2025-01-19T12:58:55.625Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Well, yes. But why not just the single vineyard designation? Why the name attached and the price is $100 less in some vintages\u2026when I referred to \u201cblend\u201d I meant perhaps other producers fruit. En Remilly is not a monopole and in checking Morris, PYCM does not have actual listed acreage there.</p>",
